title: Trains through Stafford delayed until at least 7pm
text:
National Rail @nationalrailenq Follow NEW: Delays through #Stafford until at least 19:00 details here http://t.co/yH7FXmJctI
17:08 - 22 Jul 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite A signalling near Stafford is causing delays of up to 20 minutes to trains through this station.
There is no firm estimate yet of how long disruption will last but it is likely to continue until at least 19:00.
Last updated Wed 22 Jul 2015 Travel West Midlands
